型上下文协议）远程调用的Linux性能分析工具。它提供了CPU、内存、磁盘、网络和进程分析，以及健康检查。","category":"filesystem","tags":["系统监控","性能分析","Linux运维","MCP远程调用","健康检查","DevOps"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"charlesyue-linux-profiler-mcp","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"pypi","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/yuezhongtao/linux-profiler-tool","source":"modelscope","configHint":"仅Linux主机可执行完整采集；macOS/Windows仅支持客户端连接，需部署在目标Linux节点","envSchema":{"PYTHONPATH":{"description":"/path/to/linux-profiler-tool/src","type":"string"}},"envRequired":["PYTHONPATH"],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["AI运维助手","服务器健康巡检","SRE自动化诊断"]},{"serverId":"linyufeng9468-linyufeng","friendlyName":"Moda多智能体框架","friendlyNameEn":"linyufeng","description":"面向MCP生态的Python多智能体开发库，提供标准化Agent/Environment抽象与MCP适配层，支持快速构建可组合、可观测的智能体系统。","descriptionEn":"# moda-agents\n\n## 介绍\n`moda-agents` 是一个用于创建和管理多代理系统的库。它允许开发者定义不同类型的代理，并通过简单的接口与它们进行交互。\n\n## 安装\n要安装 `moda-agents`，请使用 pip：\nbash\npip install moda-agents\n\n\n## 快速开始\n以下是一个简单的示例，展示如何使用 `moda-agents` 创建一个基本的代理系统：\n\n### 导入必要的模块\npython\nfrom moda_agents import Agent, Environment\n\n\n### 定义代理\npython\nclass MyAgent(Agent):\n    def __init__(self, name):\n        super().__init__(name)\n    \n    def act(self, observation):\n        # 根据观察采取行动\n        return \"action\"\n\n\n### 定义环境\npython\nclass MyEnvironment(Environment):\n    def __init__(self):\n        super().__init__()\n    \n    def step(self, action):\n        # 执行动作并返回新的观察结果、奖励等\n        return \"observation\", 1.0, False, {}\n    \n    def reset(self):\n        # 重置环境到初始状态\n        return \"initial_observation\"\n\n\n### 创建代理和环境实例\npython\nagent = MyAgent(\"my_agent\")\nenvironment = MyEnvironment()\n\n\n### 运行模拟\npython\nobservation = environment.reset()\nfor _ in range(10):\n    action = agent.act(observation)\n    observation, reward, done, info = environment.step(action)\n    if done:\n        break\n\n\n## 高级用法\n更多高级功能和配置选项，请参阅[官方文档](https://example.com/moda-agents/docs)。\n\n## 贡献\n我们欢迎任何形式的贡献！如果您发现了问题或有改进建议，请提交一个 [issue](https://github.com/example/moda-agents/issues) 或 [pull request](https://github.com/example/moda-agents/pulls)。\n\n## 许可证\n`moda-agents` 在 MIT 许可证下发布。详情请见 [LICENSE](https://github.com/example/moda-agents/blob/main/LICENSE) 文件。","category":"filesystem","tags":["多智能体","Agent框架","MCP适配","Python库","强化学习","模块化设计"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"bing-cn-mcp","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/linyufeng9468/moda-agents","source":"modelscope","configHint":"纯Python实现，无外部服务依赖；文档链接为占位符，实际需参考GitHub仓库","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["AI工作流编排","多角色协同Agent","教育科研实验平台"]},{"serverId":"sd3500550-lingjingTest1","friendlyName":"灵境测试桩","friendlyNameEn":"sd3500550-lingjingTest1","description":"MCP兼容性验证用基础服务桩，提供标准Ping/Pong与元数据接口，用于快速校验Agent连接性与协议握手能力。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["协议测试","MCP桩服务","连接验证","开发辅助","轻量Mock","调试工具"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"sd3500550-lingjingTest1","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"http://ja7f29dc.natappfree.cc","source":"modelscope","configHint":"无业务逻辑，仅响应预设JSON-RPC格式，适合CI/CD集成","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["MCP协议验证","Agent集成测试","自动化冒烟测试"]},{"serverId":"@spences10-mcp-memory-libsql","friendlyName":"LibSQL语义记忆库","friendlyNameEn":"MCP-LibSQL内存搜索服务","description":"基于libSQL构建的轻量嵌入式向量数据库服务，支持结构化实体+非结构化语义联合检索，适用于本地化知识中枢建设。","descriptionEn":"# 翻译\n一个高性能的MCP服务器，利用libSQL实现持久内存和向量搜索功能，能够高效地